prompt_template:
Write essential safety guidelines and best practices for laser cleaning {material} surfaces. Target audience: {target_audience} in {industry_focus}.

Requirements:
- Exactly {word_target} words
- Authoritative, safety-focused tone
- Cover personal protective equipment (PPE) requirements
- Include ventilation and fume extraction needs for {material}
- Mention laser safety classifications and regulations
- Address material-specific hazards when cleaning {material}
- Include training and certification requirements
- Technical depth: {technical_depth}
- Natural voice target: {natural_voice_target}
- Do not use headers or bullet lists
- Write in clear, instructional paragraphs

Content quality must meet threshold: {content_quality_threshold}
